Your Rights and Choices
9.1 Access and Correction:
You have the right to access and update your personal information stored by our App. If you believe that any information we hold about you is inaccurate, incomplete, or outdated, please contact us to request corrections.

9.2 Data Portability:
Upon request, we will provide you with a copy of your personal information in a structured, commonly used, and machine-readable format, to the extent feasible. You may also request that we transmit this information to another data controller where technically feasible.

9.3 Opt-Out:
You have the right to opt-out of receiving promotional communications from us. You can do so by following the unsubscribe instructions provided in the communication or by contacting us directly.

9.4 Do Not Track:
Our App does not currently respond to "Do Not Track" signals from web browsers. However, you may adjust your browser settings to block certain tracking technologies or configure your device settings to limit data collection and sharing.

International Data Transfers
Our App is operated globally, and your personal information may be transferred to and processed in countries outside of your own. These countries may have data protection laws that are different from your jurisdiction. By using our App, you consent to the transfer of your personal information to any country where we operate and the use and disclosure of your information as described in this Privacy Policy.

Third-Party Links and Services
Our App may contain links to third-party websites or services that are not operated or controlled by us. This Privacy Policy does not apply to those third-party websites or services. We recommend that you review the privacy policies of any third-party websites or services that you visit or use.

California Privacy Rights
If you are a California resident, you may have certain additional rights under the California Consumer Privacy Act (CCPA). For more information about your rights and how to exercise them, please refer to our separate California Privacy Notice, which is available on our website.

Consent to Transfer
By using our App or providing us with your personal information, you consent to the collection, use, and disclosure of your information as outlined in this Privacy Policy. You also consent to the transfer of your personal information to other countries for processing and storage.

Severability
If any provision of this Privacy Policy is found to be unlawful, void, or unenforceable, the remaining provisions shall remain in effect and continue to be binding.

